tool_description: An api that returns latest Nairobi Stock Exchange(NSE) stock prices.
name: Nairobi-Stock-Exchange-(NSE)
title: Nairobi-Stock-Exchange-(NSE)

api_list.name: Get a single stock
api_list.description: This endpoint will return the stocks that match the word given as a query parameter.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://nairobi-stock-exchange-nse.p.rapidapi.com/stocks/Safaricom"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "nairobi-stock-exchange-nse.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
